nk's unit structure offers prompt decision-making and low administrative overhead within its single office, Jamuna Bank's branch banking model is economically superior for widespread market penetration. Jamuna Bank's capacity to drive massive financial growth and ensure system security makes it a far more powerful and robust vehicle for national economic development."
