ofile within one physical office space, making it highly vulnerable to localized economic shocks, which increases its risk of insolvency.5. Conclusion:\n\nIn conclusion, while Ichamati Bank Ltd. may achieve success within its immediate local boundary due to low administrative overhead, its macro-level economic impact is minimal. Kushiyara Bank Ltd.’s extensive branch infrastructure, superior capital mobilization, international reach, and robust risk management framework make it a far more powerful and vital vehicle for driving national economic development and gross domestic product (GDP) growth."
