its.5. Conclusion:\n\nIn conclusion, transitioning from a rigid, single-industry niche bank into a full-service commercial bank is an excellent strategic move. By utilizing its idle liquidity to serve the wider public, Silonia Bank will successfully drive deposit accumulation and loan growth, ensuring long-term institutional profitability and commercial success."
