ersely, 'Q' Bank's risk is entirely concentrated in one area, making it highly vulnerable to localized shocks.5. Conclusion:\n\nIn conclusion, while 'Q' Bank offers helpful, personalized financial services within its immediate neighborhood, its structural limitations prevent it from driving macro-level economic transformation. 'P' Bank’s superior capital mobilization, nationwide network, and global operational capacity make it an indispensable engine for accelerating trade, commerce, and national gross domestic product (GDP) growth."
