bank from sudden insolvency. Conversely, Mahananda Bank's entire risk profile is concentrated within its single location, making it highly vulnerable to localized economic shocks.5. Conclusion:\n\nIn conclusion, while Mahananda Bank may successfully serve its immediate community, its structural limits prevent it from driving macro-level economic transformation. Chitra Bank Ltd.’s superior capital collection capacity, nationwide and global branch network, and robust risk management framework make it a far more powerful and vital vehicle for national economic development."
