o specialized development sectors.\n\n* Geographical Penetration: The branch banking system allows commercial PLCs to set up desks in remote upazilas while maintaining centralized corporate governance, making them the most visible financial structures in the nation. Therefore, Mr. Majid's assumption is entirely accurate."
