ection and domestic remittance processing, reducing delays in her supply chain cycles.\n\n* E-Commerce Compatibility: Modern online businesses depend heavily on integrated core banking networks (CBS) spread across multiple logistics hubs, a feature native to countrywide branch institutions like Alpha Bank. Therefore, her financial shift is entirely logical."
