                                "question": "What is an endowment insurance policy?",
                                "answer": "An endowment insurance policy is a life insurance contract where the insurer guarantees to pay a specified sum assured to the policyholder if they survive a fixed term of years, or to their nominee if the insured passes away before the term expires."
                        },
